data.description: Welcome to a slice of heaven in the sought after community of Greenleaf in Westminster! This stunning property is going on the market to seek your offer. The amenity list is not a short order. This property is nestled on Cindy Lane and boasts a gorgeous 1-acre lot. Attached to the home is a spacious 2 car garage. The lot includes an inground pool for your summer enjoyment! The pool just received a new liner 1 year ago. The pool is equipped with a pool deck for relaxing under an umbrella on those hot summer days. As you head inside, there is 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms on the upper floor and 1 bedroom and half bathroom on the lower floor. An open and large living area/dining room combo for peaceful living. On the lower floor there is a large game room, bedroom, half bath, and large laundry room. Notable upgrades on the home include updated bathrooms, roof, windows, and a new pressure tank. Windows and roof were redone in 2014. If this property interests you, please book a private showing!
